  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > About Hell's Descent </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start your roguelite adventure as a sorceresses that wields the arcane elements of fire, ice, lightning and more, acquire talents and find new gear! You must survive the relentless enemies of hell and defeat the seven deadly sins. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Hell's Descent, death is not the end but a chance to grow stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Features </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Over 40 spells and buffs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 different elemental forms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equipment system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Boss Fights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talent system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless Mode</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055000/extras/bd310bbba80f22727a5c0ae4df511a20.gif?t=1745851013\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055000/extras/bd310bbba80f22727a5c0ae4df511a20.poster.avif?t=1745851013\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055000/extras/4e8bb572b8c454fa87a3ab0fffd667bf.apng?t=1745851013\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055000/extras/4e8bb572b8c454fa87a3ab0fffd667bf.poster.avif?t=1745851013\" class=\"bb_img\" width=128 height=112 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055000/extras/5f5c1a846a7a590f9800d528fd3c4fb9.apng?t=1745851013\"><img src=\"https://shared.akama